Biography:
I started Private Servers around May or March..I liked helping people alot. I cannot host but i can help :)
Mostly that:
I thank Digzey for helping me alot :D
Hey people,
Project Npc source is soon going to be released... So by that time i am going to start a new development team,
This development team is dedicated to:
DIgzey and to Ric914 the awesome private server creator.
Stuff already in source:
When 99 u get skill capes (thanks ric914) Already Put in Test account for everyone to use, Their will be alot of different compilers i AM ADDING A LAG HANDLER THAT WILL REDUCE LAG UP TO 90% Removed all the abby demons from Ardougne and made alot of white knights
Client:
For a PK Server that i wish we could make I want to make a client for it.. 377 cache with all the modern sprites and everything Alot of coloured Phats Alot of Coloured Armour and Weaponry
I want to make this a very special server..
BUT we need a hoster/ 24hour will be great..
Who hosts for us will get:
Admin Rights Forum Rights (the one i'm still making) Exclusive rights to executive edition server that I wouldnt mind making :)
Milestones:
About 5 minigames Server holds up to atleast 130 people Skill Levels is hard like in real RS Maybe even buy a website A forum (if we save enough vbulletin) Google ads Kontera in-text ads Many Many More! Once we get our own website..Members server, Premium Members
NOTE: No one will pay to get on members etcu will have to earn your respect to log in to them :) Full SPECIALS
Who wants to join please ask here..
There are many OPEN SPOTS:
Testers Coders Client etc GFX SPrites Models Test Crasher
Please PM me for my email to talk more privately with codes and such
Server Source: Ricscape V3
Thanks, Megapkscape
